                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-11-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 18, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Assure President commencement formal negotiations hitherto prevented by
                    circumstances beyond my control. Secretary of state for foreign affairs just
                    returned. Shall proceed promptly as possible. Good reason to expect efficient
                    cooperation.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
